HEADWORD: Highbinder
<hw>High"bind`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A ruffian; one
who hounds, or spies upon, another; app. esp. to the members of certain
alleged societies among the Chinese.</def> <mark>[U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

